
Backend Package - Environment Variables
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:5432/database
JWT_SECRET=your-jwt-secret
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=your-refresh-secret
EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your-service-id
